snippet.title: Mackenzie Turner Roblox
snippet.description:
HI FRIENDS and WELCOME TO MY ROBLOX GAMING YOUTUBE CHANNEL!!!

My name is Mackenzie Turner and I am a 22 year old cotton candy, ice cream and unicorn loving girl from Vancouver, Canada! I love playing Roblox, it's my favorite video game! I will be playing Roblox Brookhaven to make daily Brookhaven RP videos! Some of my favorite Roblox Brookhaven RP videos to make are Birth to Death, The Hated Child, Princess, and Adopted roleplays! 

I love spreading happiness and making all of you guys laugh with my loud voice, sorry in advanced but I scream ALOT!
